ent.%20The%20First%20Information%20Report%20or%20FIR%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20name%20Bhole%20Baba%2C%20whose%20original%20name%20is%20Suraj%20Pal%20Singh%2C%20as%20an%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20they%20are%20probing%20the%20role%20of%20the%20local%20administration%20and%20the%20organisers.%C2%A0Permission%20was%20granted%20for%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20but%20more%20than%202.5%20lakh%20devotees%20attended%20the%20event%2C%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20organisers%20hid%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20devotees%20coming%20to%20the%20'satsang'%20while%20seeking%20permission%2C%20did%20not%20cooperate%20in%20traffic%20management%20and%20hid%20evidence%20after%20the%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClips%20before%20the%20stampede%20showed%20people%20in%20a%20large%20'shamiana'%2C%20listening%20to%20Bhole%20Baba.%20The%20'baba'%20sat%20before%20them%20on%20a%20throne-like%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyewitness%20said%20after%20the%20satsang%20ended%2C%20several%20devotees%20rushed%20towards%20the%20exit%2C%20while%20others%20moved%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20to%20collect%20the%20soil%20the%20preacher%20had%20walked%20on%20-%20causing%20a%20big%20crowd%20build-up%20in%20a%20small%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20the%20crowd%20running%20in%20the%20water%20and%20mud-filled%20fields%20behind%20baba's%20car%20was%20forcibly%20stopped%20by%20the%20organising%20committee%20with%20sticks%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20crowd%20kept%20increasing%20and%20women%2C%20children%2C%20and%20men%20kept%20getting%20crushed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each%20has%20been%20announced%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20dead%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20for%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20incident%20and%2C%20on