he%20Indian%20team%20got%20the%20thumbs%20up%20from%20the%20third%20umpire%20on%20the%20catch%2C%20there%20are%20some%20who%20continue%20to%20question%20the%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaims%20have%20been%20made%20that%20the%20boundary%20rope%20was%20pushed%20by%20feet%20before%20Surya%20perfectly%20executed%20the%20catch%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20white%20marking%20line%20was%20visible%20before%20the%20skirting.%20However%2C%20the%20claim%20has%20been%20debunked%20by%20former%20India%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aakash%20Chopra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F597-aakash-chopra-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAakash%20Chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20asked%20doubters%20to%20'push%20their%20brains%20a%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20said%20the%20original%20white%20line%20was%20visible%20and%20it%20means%20the%20skirting%20would%20have%20been%20pushed%20behind%20with%20the%20feet.%20Then%20I%20say%2C%20nothing%20was%20pushed%2C%20push%20your%20brain%20a%20little.%20Open%20your%20mind%20a%20little%20and%20understand%20the%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBHSeERxcEjI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%20got%20the%20best%20view%20of%20Surya%20Kumar%20Yadav%20catch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FT20WorldCup2024%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23T20WorldCup2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2ON6CFxawz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2ON6CFxawz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ctrl%20C%20Ctrl%20Memes%20(%40Ctrlmemes_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCtrlmemes_%2Fstatus%2F1808114487964152140%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20explained%20that%20though%20the%20line%20is%20considered%20the%20boundary%2C%20but%20its%20validity%20varies%20as%20matches%20aren't%20played%20on%20same%20pitches%20in%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20absolutely%20correct%20that%20the%20line%20is%20considered%20the%20boundary%20but%20do%20you%20know%20why%20the%20line%20was%20ahead%20of%20the%20skirting%3F%20It's%20because%20there%20are%20many%20pitches%20on%20the%20ground.%20So%20when%20the%20match%20shifts%20from%20one%20pitch%20to%20another%2C%20the%20boundary%20ropes%20are%20adjusted%2C%20and%20this%20was%20not%20the%20first%20match%20to%20be%20played%20in%20Barbados%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20markings%20were%20done%20for%20the%20original%20pitch%2C%20and%20then%20you%20changed%20them%20because%20the%20ground%20dimensions%20are%20going%20to%20change.%20The%20moment%20they%20change%2C%20those%20lines%20are%20left%20behind%2C%20and%20that's%20about%20it%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20those%20who%20feel%20Suryakumar%20intentionally%20pushed%20the%20skirting%20back%20using%20his%20feet.%20But%2C%20the%20claim%20has%20been%20rubbished%20by%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuryakumar%20Yadav%20took%20the%20catch%2C%20he%20was%20inside%2C%20he%20threw%20the%20ball%20up%20when%20he%20was%20going%20outside%2C%20and%20then%20he%20caught%20the%20ball%20after%20coming%20back.%20Everything%20was%20absolutely%20clear.%20There%20was%20no%20angle%20which%20didn't%20show%20it%20with%20clarity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20enough%20cameras.%20It's%20the%20truth%20with%20every%20international%20game.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20had%2026%20cameras%20in%20the%20Bengal%20Pro%20T20%20league%2C%20and%20this%20was%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup.%20There%20are%2030-40%20cameras%2C%20nothing%20is%20hidden%20from%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20conc