aina%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F722-suresh-raina-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuresh%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuvraj%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F456-yuvraj-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuvraj%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shoaib%20Malik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F382-shoaib-malik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Malik%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20also%20present.%20Virat%20Kohli%20was%20going%20through%20a%20similar%20phase.%20The%20Team%20India%20manager%20walked%20up%20to%20Dhoni%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20drop%20Virat%20Kohli%20from%20the%20final%20ODI%20of%20the%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Akmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDhoni%20replied%20saying%2C%20'I%20haven't%20gone%20home%20for%20six%20months.%20Why%20don't%20you%20book%20my%20tickets%20too%20along%20with%20Virat's%3F'%20Then%20the%20manager%20allowed%20him%20to%20play%20whoever%20he%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20continued%20Akmal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni's%20sharp%20response%20to%20the%20question%20of%20dropping%20Kohli%20had%20left%20the%20Pakistan%20wicket-keeper%20batsman%20shocked.%20Akmal%20said%20that%20Dhoni%20had%20a%20simple%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20is%20our%20best%20batter.%20Why%20should%20we%20drop%20him%20if%20he%20fails%20for%203-4%20games%3F%26quot%3B%20Akmal%20recalled%20Dhoni%20telling%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAll%20those%20Virat%20Kohli%20fans%20who%20hate%20MS%20Dhoni%20%2CSee%20how%20Dhoni%20supported%20Kohli%20in%20his%20bad%20times.%3Cbr%3E%5CnFormer%20Pakistan%20player%20Umar%20Akmal%20told%20how%20Dhoni%20supported%20Virat%20Kohli%20in%20his%20lean%20patch%20and%20saved%20him%20from%20being%20dropped%20from%20the%20team.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F