%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20creates%20an%20immunity%20that%20is%20so%20ill-defined%20and%20so%20unmoored%20from%20any%20agreed-upon%20constitutional%20text%20or%20history%2C%20that%20there%20is%20no%20way%20of%20knowing%20its%20outer%20limits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20leaving%20so%20much%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20outer%20limits%20means%2C%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20that%20those%20outer%20limits%20don't%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpiece-of-evidence-can-now-scuttle-trump-hush-money-conviction-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719960710000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668480e41f0c1cd6d731063c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpiece-of-evidence-can-now-scuttle-trump-hush-money-conviction-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20SCOTUS%20immunity%20decision%2C%20it%20may%20not%20take%20much%20to%20force%20a%20hush-money%20retrial.%20An%20ethics%20form%20the%20DA%20showed%20jurors%20in%20May%20might%20do%20the%20trick.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpiece-of-evidence-can-now-scuttle-trump-hush-money-conviction-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Robert%20Towne%2C%20Writer%20of%20%E2%80%98Chinatown%2C%E2%80%99%20Dies%20at%2089%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719959934000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FGettyImages-467548508-1-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236059676%26preview%3Dtrue%26preview_id%3D1236059676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Writer-director%20