%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fland%2F2024%2F05%2F31%2Fa-lighter-high-tech-abrams-tank-is-taking-shape%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20to%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%20May%20that%20the%20Army%20had%20awarded%20a%20contract%20to%20Abrams%20manufacturer%20General%20Dynamics%20Land%20Systems%20(GDLS)%20to%20start%20developing%20requirements%20for%20what%20it's%20calling%20the%20M1E3%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20Abrams%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReached%20for%20details%20on%20the%20contract%2C%20GDLS%20referred%20all%20questions%20to%20the%20Army's%20PEO%20Ground%20Combat%20Systems%2C%20which%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Sandboxx%20News'%20queries.%20While%20the%20Defense%20Department%20published%20award%20notices%20for%20several%20smaller%20Abrams%20contract%20modifications%20in%20May%2C%20it%20appears%20the%20details%20of%20this%20design%20contract%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20begins%20a%20new%20era%20of%20development%20for%20the%20Abrams%2C%20and%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20decades%3A%20the%20last%20full%20M1A2%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limaohio.com%2Ftop-stories%2F2023%2F03%2F10%2Freal-wheels-lima-where-tanks-are-made%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20off%20production%20lines%20in%201996%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%2C%20the%20task%20of%20rolling%20out%20a%20modernized%20tank%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20needs%20to%20cut%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fland%2F2024%2F05%2F31%2Fa-lighter-high-tech-abrams-tank-is-taking-shape%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2010%20tons%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20its%20fighting%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20is%20formidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20M1A2%20Abrams%20is%20in%20a%20weight%20class%20of%20its%20own%20among%20the%20world's%20leading%20tanks%3A%20the%20current%20variant%2C%20the%20SEPv3%2C%2