B%20movie%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20make%20north%20of%20%2465%20million%20domestically.%20(Right%20now%2C%20it's%20made%20%2411%20million.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20even%20started%20talking%20about%20profit%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241e83c85-9283-4ac5-9892-1bc1471f9349%5C%22%3ECostner%20needs%20a%20huge%20%26quot%3BPay%201%26quot%3B%20deal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kevin%20Costner%20in%20a%20cowboy%20hat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66829eb31f0c1cd6d7301eed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Costner%20in%20%26quot%3BHorizon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECostner%20believes%20in%20the%20long%20game.%20When%20he%20made%20the%20box%20office%20bomb%20%26quot%3BWaterworld%26quot%3B%20back%20in%201995%2C%20which%20was%20the%20most%20expensive%20movie%20ever%20made%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20took%20ancillary%20deals%20like%20paid%20cable%20and%20DVD%20sales%20to%20finally%20break%20even.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fscottmendelson%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2Fwaterworld-starring-kevin-costner-was-the-biggest-box-office-bomb-that-wasnt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20took%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDVD%20sales%20have%20fallen%20off%20the%20map%20since%20the%20mid-1990s%2C%20so%20Costner%20can't%20lean%20into%20that.%20Instead%2C%20he'll%20have%20to%20land%20a%20major%20deal%20with%20a%20streamer%20or%20cable%20company%20for%20the%20movie's%20post-theatrical%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20%26quot%3BPay%201.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPay%201%20deals%20kick%20in%20after%20a%20movie%20is%20through%20with%20its%20Video-On-Demand%20option.%20Deals%20can%20range%20from%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20to%20as%20high%20as%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20pay%20varies%2C%20the%20producer%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20Costner%20could%20negotiate%20a%20deal%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20millions%20because%20of%20his%20star%20power%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20franchise%20and%20not%20just%20the%20first%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20sweetens%20the%20pot%20for%20a%20streamer%20is%20that%20Costner%20is%20a%20fixture%20in%20Westerns.%20As%20the%20face%20of%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%2C%26quot%3B%20(at%20least%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyellowstone-timeline-of-controversy-criticism-conflict-kevin-costner-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euntil%20he%20quit%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20fans%20of%20that%20show%20love%20him.%20A%20streamer%20could%20be%20convinced%20that%20the%20true%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20audience%20didn't%20show%20up%20to%20theaters%20and%2C%20due%20to%20its%20three-hour%20runtime%2C%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20movie%20to%20hit%20streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20windy%20road%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20path%20for%20Costner%20to%20come%20out%20of%20%26quot%3BHorizon%26quot%3B%20without%20a%20major%20loss.%20The%20only%20problem%20is%20that%20there%20are%20more%20installments%20on%20the%20way%2C%20which%20means%20more%20money%20needs%20to%20be%20spent%20first%3A%20%26quot%3BHorizon%3A%20Chapter%202%26quot%3B%20opens%20August%2016%2C%20%26quot%3BChapter%203%26quot%3B%20has%20begun%20principal%20photography%20for%20a%20May%202024%20release%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BChapter%204%26quot%3B%20is%20in%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20contacted%20reps%20for%20Warner%20Bros.%20and%20Kevin%20Costner%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20story%20but%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-costner-horizon-box-office-numbers-break-even-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719955118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt