C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjeffrose.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Rose%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20review%20my%20business%20and%20finances%20and%20suggest%20new%20and%20practical%20ways%20to%20earn%20passive%20income%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20Here%20are%20his%20top%20recommendations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Consider%20investing%20in%20more%20dividend-paying%20stocks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20Rose%20asked%20was%20whether%20or%20not%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-invest-in-stocks%5C%22%3Estarted%20investing%20in%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20pay%20dividends.%20When%20I%20audited%20my%20investment%20portfolios%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20I%20had%20not%20bought%20very%20many%20of%20these%20stocks%20and%20was%20potentially%20missing%20out%20on%20recurring%20passive%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDividend-paying%20stocks%20reward%20shareholders%20by%20paying%20out%20a%20percent%20of%20their%20earnings%2C%20on%20a%20quarterly%20basis%2C%20as%20a%20token%20of%20appreciation%20for%20investing%20and%20owning%20their%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20does%20come%20with%20risks.%20%26quot%3BGetting%20paid%20dividends%20from%20a%20stock%20isn't%20guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20company%20could%20go%20bankrupt%20or%20no%20longer%20be%20profitable.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20benefit%20of%20this%20passive%20income%20stream%20is%20that%20if%20the%20company%20is%20doing%20well%20and%20paying%20out%20consistent%20dividends%2C%20you're%20also%20benefiting%20from%20the%20stock%20price%20rising%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20people%20making%20money%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20because%20the%20stock%20price%20is%20going%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20the%20dividend%20earnings%20on%20top%20of%20that.%20It's%20like%20getting%20your%20cake%20and%20eating%20it%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsofi-invest-review%5C%22%3ESoFi%20Invest%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20named%20Business%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-investment-apps-for-beginners%5C%22%3Ebest%20investing%20app%20for%20beginners%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202024.%20Sofi%20provides%20straightforward%20investment%20strategies%20and%20commission-free%20trades.%20Learn%20more%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsofi-invest-review%5C%22%3ESoFi%20Invest%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Look%20into%20putting%20money%20into%20more%20REITs%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20shared%20with%20Rose%20that%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20earn%20passive%20income%20through%20real%20estate%20but%20didn't%20have%20the%20capital%20to%20buy%20a%20rental%20property.%20Instead%2C%20I%20recently%20started%20putting%20a%20little%20money%20into%20real%20estate%20investment%20trusts%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-a-reit%5C%22%3EREITs%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20see%20if%20that%20could%20generate%20passive%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20shared%20that%20REITS%20can%20be%20a%20great%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-invest-in-real-estate-make-money%5C%22%3Einvest%20in%20real%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20purchasing%20or%20managing%20a%20property%20of%20your%20own.%20When%20you%20put%20money%20into%20one%20of%20these%20trusts%2C%20you%20are%20investing%20in%20a%20company%20that%20already%20owns%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BREITs%20typically%20can%20bring%20in%20a%20higher%20return%20than%20dividend-paying%20stocks.%20However%2C%20they%20could%20come%20with%20more%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20more%20volatile%20investment%20because%20the%20real%20estate%20market%20can%20fluctuate%20depending%20on%20many%20factors%2C%20like%20the%20economy%20or%20interest%20rates.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20you%20could%20potentially%20get%20a%20bigger%20dividend%20yield%20than%20you%20would%20by%20investing%20in%20other%20stocks%2C%20the%20biggest%20risk%20of%20investing%20in%20a%20REIT%20is%20seeing%20the%20money%20you%20put%20in%20drop%20suddenly%20or%20more%20harshly%20than%20it%20could%20if%20you%20invested%20in%20a%20blue%20chip%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20others%20who%20don't%20have%20the%20money%20on%20hand%20to%20buy%20property%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20created%20a%20list%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-real-estate-investing-platforms%5C%22%3Ebest%20real%20estate%20investing%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Sell%20more%20digital%20products%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20looking%20over%20my%20business%2C%20Rose%20suggested%20another%20opportunity%20that%20I%20could%20take%20advantage%20of%20for%20passive%20income%3A%20selling%20more%20digital%20products.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20created%20and%20sold%20online%20courses%20as%20a%20passive%20income%20stream.%20He%20suggested%20expanding%20and%20changing%20my%20offerings%20and%20selling%20ebooks%2C%20PDFs%2C%20or%20digital%20workbooks%20instead%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20live%20in%20a%20world%20of%20digital%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said.%20%26quot%3BThink%20about%20how%20to%20take%20your%20skills%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20business%20services%20and%20create%20step-by-step%20guides%2C%20checklists%2C%20digital%20journals%2C%20or%20planners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20courses%20are%20outdated%20and%20I've%20seen%20other%20people%20make%20passive%20income%20selling%20these%20types%20of%20products%20on%20Etsy%2C%20I%20made%20doing%20this%20a%20goal%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20benefit%20is%20that%20once%20you've%20created%20these%20digital%20products%2C%20there's%20minimal%20upkeep%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20risk%20is%20that%20to%20earn%20the%20income%2C%20you%20have%20to%20invest%20time%20in%20marketing%20or%20have%20an%20existing%20audience%20ready%20and%20interested%20in%20buying%20what%20you%20create.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Tap%20into%20what%20you%20already%20have%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20person%20is%20eager%20to%20introduce%20a%20new%20stream%20of%20passive%20income%20into%20their%20life%2C%20they%20should%20first%20look%20at%20what%20skills%20or%20assets%20they%20already%20have%20that%20can%20be%20monetized.%20%26quot%3BAudit%20what%20you're%20already%20working%20with%20and%20see%20how%20you%20can%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20passive%20income%20stream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20rent%20out%20items%20you%20own%2C%20create%20digital%20products%2C%20or%20write%20an%20ebook%20to%20sell%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20case%2C%20one%20missed%20opportunity%20for%20passive%20income%20we%20discovered%20involved%20the%20traffic%20I'm%20already%20getting%20to%20my%20business%20website.%20After%20speaking%20to%20Rose%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20run%20Google%20ads%20on%20my%20website%20and%20last%20month%20was%20able%20to%20bring%20in%20%24390%20in%20passive%20income%20just%20through%20those%20ads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20passive%20income%20stream%20will%20vary%20month%20to%20month%20based%20on%20how%20much%20traffic%20my%20website%20gets%2C%20it%20could%20bring%20in%20an%20extra%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20this%20year.%20As%20a%20solopreneur%2C%20new%20streams%20of%20income%20keep%20my%20business%20afloat%2C%20and%20the%20passive%20ones%20give%20me%20time%20to%20enjoy%20other%20aspects%20of%20my%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20st