e%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brie%20Schmidt%20on%20a%20widmill%20balcony%20in%20Deift%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6682e439c31eb990ea2fbd7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20an%20American%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20was%20able%20to%20move%20to%20Europe.%20%3Cp%3EBrie%20Schmidt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-about-moving-to-japan-with-family-from-us-american%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20who%20lived%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20about%20six%20years%20until%20I%20started%20to%20feel%20lonely%20and%20lost.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20sold%20my%20house%20in%20Tokyo%20and%20traveled%20around%20Europe%20until%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20used%20a%20special%20treaty%20to%20get%20citizenship%20in%20Europe%20and%20I'm%20happy%20living%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20in%20January%202022%2C%20it%20hit%20me%3A%20I%20had%20outgrown%20my%20life%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-went-to-high-school-in-japan-worth-it-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20living%20in%20Tokyo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20still%20felt%20like%20a%20fish%20out%20of%20water%20after%20six%20years%2C%20despite%20my%20many%20attempts%20at%20mastering%20Japanese%2C%20perfecting%20my%20bow%2C%20and%20learning%20how%20to%20(politely)%20push%20my%20way%20through%20the%20crowded%20rush-hour%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20few%20years%20in%20Japan%20were%20exciting%20and%20dreamy%2C%20what%20many%20would%20expect%20when%20they%20imagine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-moving-to-japan-tokyo-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20visited%20stunning%20shrines%20and%20temples%2C%20sipped%20oolong-hai%20cocktails%20with%20friends%20in%20izakayas%2C%20spent%20hours%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-public-toilets-state-of-the-art-designs-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20the%20streets%20of%20Shibuya%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20back%20then%2C%20Japan%20felt%20like%20my%20playground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22404a50f4-d14b-43b5-b5f2-a8fdbe7f54ed%5C%22%3EMy%20experience%20in%20Japan%20changed%20with%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overview%20of%20people%20walking%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6682d9561f0c1cd6d7303abe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJapan%20sometimes%20felt%20like%20a%20lonely%20place%20for%20me.%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A9%20Marco%20Bottigelli%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20some%20of%20the%20drawbacks%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Land%20of%20the%20Rising%20Sun%20started%20to%20wear%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20quiet%20and%20inconspicuous%20I%20tried%20to%20be%2C%20I%20received%20stares%20(and%20occasionally%20glares)%20in%20my%20suburban%20neighborhood%20because%20of%20how%20much%20I%20stood%20out%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20Japanese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Fthe-world-factbook%2Fcountries%2Fjapan%2Fsummaries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%202.5%25%20of%20the%20country's%20population%20is%20non-Japanese%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Although%20Japanese%20culture%20is%20fascinating%2C%20I%20started%20to%20miss%20diversity%20and%20multiculturalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20Japan%20also%20felt%20increasingly%20lonely%20with%20each%20year%20I%20stayed.%20For%20one%2C%20Japanese%20society%20is%20known%20for%20being%20reserved%2C%20and%20striking%20up%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20stranger%20in%20big%20cities%20like%20Tokyo%20is%20often%20viewed%20as%20a%20transgression%20against%20the%20order%20and%20harmony%20woven%20into%20most%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20Japan%20is%20literally%20isolated%2C%20surrounded%20by%20water%20on%20all%20sides.%20This%20can%20make%20it%20challenging%20to%20get%20out%20and%20visit%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20eager%20to%20explore%20new%20places%20and%20make%20more%20connections%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Japan%20no%20longer%20seemed%20to%20align%20with%20these%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a728b81-9427-4d86-8fac-7fb6946afbf3%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20move%20to%20next%20but%20going%20back%20to%20the%20US%20didn't%20feel%20right%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20revelation%20in%20early%202022%2C%20my%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Japanese%20national%20I%20met%20within%20my%20first%20year%20in%20the%20East%20Asian%20country%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20assumed%20the%20only%20other%20option%20was%20to%20live%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20I'm%20from.%20But%20we%20struggled%20to%20settle%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-place-that-feels-like-home-in-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20city%20that%20fit%20our%20ideal%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20stall%20our%20decision%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20home%20in%20Tokyo%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-europe-with-family-life-better-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraveled%20around%20Europe%20as%20digital%20nomads%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20adventure%20began%20in%202023%20and%20included%20a%20stop%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20which%20we%20were%20surprised%20to%20discover%20felt%20like%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Amsterdam%2C%20we%20tallied%20up%20the%20perks%20that%20Japan%20lacked%3A%20multiculturalism%2C%20locals%20who%20made%20small%20talk%20with%20us%20about%20our%20little%20dog%2C%20and%20convenient%20travel%20to%20other%20countries%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20without%20the%20stares%20and%20unwanted%20attention%20I'd%20once%20received%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20refreshing%20sense%20of%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20trip%2C%20I%20also%20learned%20about%20the%20Dutch%20American%20Friendship%20Treaty%2C%20an%20agreement%20that%20allows%20American%20entrepreneurs%20to%20obtain%20residence%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20with%20little%20hassle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-europe-better-than-us-according-to-american-in-ireland-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStaying%20in%20Europe%20long-term%3C%2Fa%3E%20never%20seemed%20realistic%2C%20but%20with%20this%20program%2C%20I%20saw%20it%20could%20be%20a%20feasible%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221cb428f3-e5ae-4bd5-b601-88da1f60b6b4%5C%22%3EThe%20Netherlands%20offers%20what%20I%20had%20missed%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Panoramic%20view%20of%20buildings%20along%20the%20water%20in%20the%20Netherlands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6682d9871aace5b3ada31c46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221257%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Europe%20I%20started%20to%20realize%20maybe%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20move%20to%20the%20US%20after%20all.%3Cp%3EYasonya%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20after%20our%20trip%20to%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20the%20country%20as%20residents%20rather%20than%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20felt%20welcomed%20by%20my%20neighbors%2C%20already%20made%20friends%20from%20numerous%20countries%20and%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20even%20found%20it%20easier%20to%20visit%20my%20family%20in%20the%20US%20compared%20to%20whe