%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20have%20any%20air%20conditioning%20in%20the%20property%20as%20the%20greenery%20around%20the%20homestay%20and%20the%20natural%20materials%20keep%20it%20cool%20throughout%20the%20summers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Haneena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20various%20activities%20that%20you%20can%20do%20at%20the%20property%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20water%20bodies%20on%20our%20property.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%20two%20are%20designed%20for%20swimming.%20These%20are%20not%20conventional%20swimming%20pools%20but%20beautiful%20tropical%20ponds%20that%20are%20very%20deep.%20The%20water%E2%80%99s%20colour%20and%20the%20surroundings%20make%20for%20an%20incredible%20experience.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20also%20hosts%20workshops%20and%20events%20regularly.%20%E2%80%9CGuests%20who%20stay%20with%20us%20can%20participate%20in%20all%20these%20activities%20at%20no%20extra%20cost.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20founder%20visits%20the%20farm%20twice%20a%20day%2C%20every%20morning%20and%20evening%2C%20to%20meet%20the%20guests.%20During%20these%20visits%2C%20he%20gives%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20farm%2C%20shares%20stories%20about%20how%20the%20land%20has%20changed%2C%20and%20explains%20the%20significance%20of%20each%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuests%20can%20also%20take%20a%20landscaping%20class%20and%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20it%20from%20Mustafa%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20highlight%20is%20the%20food%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20Malabari%20cuisine%20prepared%20by%20our%20mother.%20The%20menu%20is%20never%20constant%20as%20it%20changes%20seasonally%20based%20on%20the%20availability%20of%20ingredients%2C%20with%20half%20of%20the%20raw%20materials%20grown%20on%20the%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaneena%20ensures%20that%20you%20will%20leave%20rejuvenated%20