%20the%20sustainable%20furniture%20brand%20Ombak%20which%20makes%20chairs%20out%20of%20banana%20fibre%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Shruthi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20the%20banana%20fibres%2C%20seagrass%20and%20water%20hyacinth%20are%20procured%20from%20across%20Indonesia.%20Letting%20us%20in%20on%20the%20decisions%20that%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20interesting%20choice%20of%20materials%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20natural%20fibre.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20of%20them%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20choose%20fibres%20that%20would%20be%20a%20blend%20of%20eco-friendly%20nature%20and%20good%20aesthetics.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20business%20standpoint%20too%20these%20materials%20are%20excellent.%20%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20banana%20fibre%20for%20instance.%20It%20is%20abundantly%20available%20throughout%20Asia%20and%20has%20been%20in%20use%20for%20years.%20So%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20availability%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20work%20with%20these%20materials.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F141776%2Fwater-hyacinth-organic-manure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWater%20hyacinth%3C%2Fa%3E%20shares%20a%20similar%20storyline.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20that%20in%20most%20countries%2C%20water%20hyacinth%20is%20considered%20a%20weed%20and%20its%20rapid%20growth%20often%20affects%20water%20beds%3F%20The%20plant%20forms%20sheets%20over%20the%20water%20body%2C%20preventing%20sunlight%20from%20penetrating.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShruthi%20has%20become%20adept%20at%20spotting%20value%20in%20what%20others%20might%20consider%20to%20be%20waste%2C%20and%20she%20emphasises%20that%20the%20search%20for%20such%20materials%20is%20not%20over%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20currently%20exploring%20the%20potential%20of%20paper%20and%20raffia%20palm.%20%E2%8