px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sakshi%20underwent%20more%20than%2020%20surgeries%20to%20fix%20her%20injuries%20and%20she%20says%20recovery%20is%20still%20on%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-2-1719488477-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354581%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESakshi%20underwent%20more%20than%2020%20surgeries%20to%20fix%20her%20injuries%20and%20she%20says%20recovery%20is%20still%20on%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sakshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20this%20challenging%20scene%20that%20Sakshi%20announced%20her%20decision%20to%20continue%20her%20MBBS%20studies.%20Everyone%20was%20taken%20aback%2C%20particularly%20her%20friends%2C%20colleagues%20and%20professors%2C%20she%20says%2C%20who%20thought%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20resume%20studies%20so%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20hindsight%2C%20she%20feels%20it%20was%20the%20right%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20accelerated%20my%20recovery%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20unable%20to%20hold%20a%20pen%20to%20securing%20a%20distinction%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20Sakshi%20on%20her%20feet%20took%20a%20villa