%20peace%20in%20running%20and%20has%20participated%20in%20many%20marathons%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sakshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorrowing%20from%20her%20own%20experience%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20morning%20when%20I%20wake%20up%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20back%20to%20the%20day%20before%20and%20all%20the%20things%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20do.%20Instead%2C%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20what%20I%20can%20achieve%20today.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20she%20points%20out%2C%20profound%20change%20comes%20only%20when%20you%20decide%20to%20let%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20would%20see%20people%20walking%2C%20I%20would%20often%20think%20to%20myself%20that%20they%20were%20so%20lucky.%20It%20makes%20me%20realise%20how%20we%20only%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20something%20when%20it%20is%20taken%20away%20from%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20incident%20has%20made%20me%20more%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271615%2Fdoctor-treats-patients-for-free-buys-medicines-groceries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempathetic%20towards%20my%20patients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20connected%20with%20my%20family%20and%20more%20believing%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20a%20greater%20force%20that%20has%20the%20power%20to%20get%20you%20through%20your%20toughest%20phases.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-5-1719489020.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sakshi%20Maheshwari's%20story%20is%20a%20message%20for%20every%20person%20who%20is%20going%20through%20a%20difficult%20time%20that%20persistence%20is%20key%20to%20success%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22