s%20that%20their%20trucks%20would%20be%20concealed%20by%20Dhanajay%E2%80%99s.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20spot%20where%20Dhananjay%20could%20operate%20without%20being%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20other%20food%20trucks.%20Everyone%20was%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20truck%20is%20being%20helmed%20by%20Dhanajay%20along%20with%20Rudrapratap%20Singh%20(he%2Fhim).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201170px)%20100vw%2C%201170px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0016-1-1719562806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20food%20truck%20'Sweekar'%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20actor%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0016-1-1719562806.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0016-1-1719562806-300x176.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0016-1-1719562806-500x294.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0016-1-1719562806-768x452.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240627-WA0016-1-1719562806-150x88.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354774%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20food%20truck%20%E2%80%98Sweekar%E2%80%99%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20actor%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ishnoor%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20about%20the%20experience%2C%20Dhananjay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20hate%20so%20many%20times.%20There%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%