%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354382%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVishwan%20is%20a%20honey%20farmer%20who%20earns%20lakhs%20from%20his%20farm%20where%20he%20harvests%20over%206%2C000%20bee%20boxes%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeft%20with%20no%20other%20options%2C%20he%20resorted%20to%20stealing%20food%20and%20living%20in%20treehouses%20built%20to%20observe%20animals%20that%20destroyed%20crops%20at%20night%20%E2%80%94%20all%20this%20during%20the%201970s.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20never%20stolen%20anything%20but%20I%20had%20to.%20I%20have%20only%20stolen%20food%20items%2C%20that%20too%20due%20to%20unbearable%20hunger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20time%2C%20he%20got%20caught%20while%20stealing%2C%20but%20the%20owner%20was%20a%20kind%20man.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20explained%20that%20I%20stole%20because%20of%20hunger%20and%20I%20had%20no%20one%20to%20care%20for%20me%2C%20the%20man%20asked%20him%20to%20graze%20his%20cattle%20and%20gave%20him%2015%20paise%20per%20day%20as%20a%20wage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20grazing%20cattle%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332769%2Fgeorge-remedios-plants-food-forests-trees-in-mumbai-limited-spaces-rooftop-gardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20forest%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Nilambur%2C%20he%20noticed%20honeycombs%20and%20honey%20bees%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Soon%2C%20those%20honeycombs%20became%20a%20source%20of%20filling%20his%20stomach.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20hungry%2C%20I%20collected%20honey%20and%20drank%20it.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20would%20get%20bitten%20sometimes%2C%20but%20hunger%20is%20your%20greatest%20shield%20at%20such%20times.%20One%20of%20those%20days%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20I%20keep%20them%2C%20then%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20h