worldly%20experience%20or%20formal%20education.%20There%20was%20no%20one%20to%20help%20me.%20Had%20I%20not%20found%20out%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F113516%2Fconcerned-citizens-forum-thane-takes-up-beekeeping%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20occupation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20what%20I%20would%20have%20done.%20Honey%20was%20the%20only%20kind%20of%20farming%20that%20required%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20capital.%20All%20other%20kinds%20of%20farming%20required%20lots%20of%20land%2C%20which%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20discussing%20the%20process%20of%20beekeeping%20and%20honey%20farming%2C%20Vishwan%20explains%20the%20entire%20process%20in%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-8.53.41-PM-1-1719400990-500x753.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vishwan%20currently%20sells%20harvested%20honey%20to%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20in%20Chennai%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-8.53.41-PM-1-1719400990-500x753.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-8.53.41-PM-1-1719400990-199x300.jpeg%20199w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-8.53.41-PM-1-1719400990-150x226.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-8.53.41-PM-1-1719400990.jpeg%20712w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354384%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22753%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVishwan%20currently%20s